{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_08_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 1話 おもてなしするっちゃ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は、観光大使の仕事のために山形に残った）\n（すみれの様子を見に来た訳だが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I stayed in Yamagata today for the tourism ambassador job.）\n（I came to check on Sumire… ）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2141270638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さ～～ん！\nお疲れ様です、お待ちしてました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-saaaan!\nGood work today‚ I’ve been waiting for you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9229286512,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 199.9999999999993,
          "startTime": 7.4141270638
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、わざわざ待っててくれたのか\n観光大使の仕事もあるのに、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ you were waiting for me?\nThank you‚ even though you have your tourism ambassador work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3235148431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ！　{user}さんが山形に\n来てくれて、凄く嬉しいです。待ち伏せ作戦成功です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No problem! I’m so happy that {user}-san came to Yamagata.\nOperation Stakeout was a success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.3235148431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.9235148431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんは入れ違いで\n今朝別の仕事があるので東京に戻りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rui-chan and Yu-chan left for Tokyo this morning\nFor another job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9591354294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも\n今日はここにお泊りするんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚\nAre you staying here tonight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1568481764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.0235148431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、山形にいる間はここに滞在する予定だよ\nすみれ達は、昨日泊まったんだよな。どうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I’m staying here while I’m in Yamagata.\nYou guys stayed here yesterday‚ right? How was it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9912922861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ここ、すっごくいいお宿ですよ\n温泉も気持ちいいですし、お鍋も美味しかったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! This is a really great inn.\nThe hot spring feels great‚ and the hot pot was delicious~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7246256194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "地元の素材を使った山菜鍋なんて\n東京だとなかなか食べられないですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t get to eat sansai hot pot with local ingredients\nVery often in Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8246256194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1246256194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、三人でのんびり温泉にも入れましたよ\nトリエルの大事な思い出がまた一つ増えました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And we were able to leisurely enjoy the hot spring together‚ all three of us.\nAnother precious memory for TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.7912930491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのおかげですね！\n旅館とお鍋を予約してくれて、ありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s all thanks to you‚ {user}-san!\nThank you for booking the ryokan and the hot pot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.3246266367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "喜んでもらえて俺も嬉しいよ\nトリエルの打ち上げっていったら鍋だと思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad you liked it.\nWhen I think of a TRINITYAiLE celebration‚ I think of hot pot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.6302950544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりそうですよね！\n私達も同じことを言いながらお鍋をつつきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it!\nWe said the same thing as we ate the hot pot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9969619753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.496961721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ご飯の後は温泉に入って、温泉の後は……\nふふっ、浴衣で卓球したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After dinner we went to the hot spring‚ and after the hot spring…\nFufu‚ we played table tennis in our yukata.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3302953086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "運動関係は、私達三人の中だと\n瑠依ちゃんが最強……だと思うじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to sports‚ out of the three of us‚\nRui-chan is the strongest… you’d think‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2302953086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依は運動神経がいいからなぁ\nん？　もしかして違ったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui’s got good reflexes‚\nHmm? Don’t tell me that’s not the case?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.0000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0995695117
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "なんと！　温泉ピンポン最強は、優ちゃんでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surprisingly! Yu-chan was the hot spring ping-pong champion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0995695117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.332902845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "表情が変わらないし、どこに打ち込むか分からなくて\n瑠依ちゃんがフェイントに引っかかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her expression doesn’t change‚ and you can’t tell where\nshe’s going to hit the ball‚ Rui-chan got caught by her feints…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7329030993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "気付いたら優ちゃんが勝っていたんです\n瑠依ちゃんも悔しそうだけど楽しそうでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before we knew it‚ Yu-chan had won.\nRui-chan looked frustrated but she seemed to be having fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1329030993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.8329043709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "本当に楽しかった～……\nおかげで、今日からまた、元気一杯頑張れます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so much fun~…\nThanks to that‚ I can go back to work full of energy starting today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8662364326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.6662377043
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "充実したオフを過ごせたみたいで良かったよ\nそういえば、今日からはどこに泊まるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m glad you had a fulfilling day off.\nSpeaking of which‚ where are you staying from today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.9511227813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8802509947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、実家が近いので\nしばらくは実家からお仕事に向かいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ my parents’ house is close by‚\nSo I’ll be commuting from home for a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1135830564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "チェックアウトは済んでるんですけど\n{user}さんをお迎えしたくて待ってたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve already checked out‚\nBut I was waiting to welcome you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4469163897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.5469176613
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_01-smr018.m4a",
